'''Apple Watch Series 1'''和'''Apple Watch Series 2'''是[[蘋果公司|蘋果公司]]推出的第二代[[Apple_Watch|Apple Watch]][[智慧手錶|智慧手錶]]，在2016年9月16日同時发布。<ref name="PC Magazine">{{cite news |last1 = Torres |first1 = Timothy |title = Apple Watch Series 2 vs. Samsung Gear S3: Smartwatch Smackdown |url = https://www.pcmag.com/news/347704/apple-watch-series-2-vs-samsung-gear-s3-smartwatch-smackdo |website = [[PC_Magazine|PC Magazine]] |accessdate = September 12, 2016 |archive-date = 2019-12-04 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191204014432/https://www.pcmag.com/news/347704/apple-watch-series-2-vs-samsung-gear-s3-smartwatch-smackdo |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="CNET">{{cite news |last1 = Graziano |first1 = Dan |title = Apple Watch Series 2 vs. Samsung Gear S3 vs. Fitbit vs. Android Wear vs. Garmin vs. Pebble |url = http://www.cnet.com/news/apple-watch-series-2-vs-samsung-gear-s3-vs-fitbit-vs-android-wear-vs-garmin-vs-pebble/ |website = [[CNET|CNET]] |accessdate = September 12, 2016 |archive-date = 2016-09-12 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160912080502/http://www.cnet.com/news/apple-watch-series-2-vs-samsung-gear-s3-vs-fitbit-vs-android-wear-vs-garmin-vs-pebble/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>分别使用[[Apple_S1|Apple S1]]和[[Apple_S2|Apple S2]]处理器，<ref name="apple">{{cite press release |url = https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2016/09/apple-introduces-apple-watch-series-2.html |publisher = Apple |title = Apple Introduces Apple Watch Series 2, The Ultimate Device For A Healthy Life |accessdate = September 12, 2016 |archive-date = 2020-09-15 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200915120656/https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2016/09/apple-introduces-apple-watch-series-2.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>Series 2内嵌了[[GPS|GPS]]模块，显示亮度是上一代的两倍，便于户外使用。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://support.apple.com/kb/SP746?locale=en_CA |title = Apple Watch Series 2: Technical Specifications |publisher = Apple |language = en |access-date = December 11, 2017 |archive-date = 2020-07-26 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200726083242/https://support.apple.com/kb/SP746?locale=en_CA |dead-url = no }}</ref>

== 容易混淆 ==
Apple Watch Series 1和Series 2是在同一时间发布的，都拥有比[[Apple_Watch_(第一代)|第一代Apple Watch]]更快的处理器，但Series 2有GPS模块、真防水功能（50米）和1000尼特亮度的螢幕，CPU時脈也略快；Series 1对比第一代只有一点小改动，第一代Apple Watch通常被称为Series 0，但苹果公司官方并没有这个说法。

